===Proper noun===
'''Matthew'''

#A male [[given name]].  Short form: [[Matt]].
# (''Bible'') [[w:Matthew the Evangelist|Matthew the Evangelist]], also called Levi, a publican or tax-collector at Capernaum and credited with the authorship of the Gospel of Matthew.
# The [[w:Gospel of Matthew|Gospel of Matthew]], traditionally the first of the four [[gospel]]s, a [[book]] attributed to Matthew the Evangelist.


